### AI Task Manager API — VS Code REST Client
### Install the "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client) to run these.
### Click "Send Request" above any request block.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5099
@contentType = application/json

# ─── Step 1: Register ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Register a new account
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "Secure@Pass1"
}

###

# Grab the token from the register response
@token = {{register.response.body.data.accessToken}}


# ─── Step 2: Login ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Login with demo account (seeded on startup)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "demo@aitaskmanager.dev",
  "password": "Demo@123!"
}

###

@demoToken = {{login.response.body.data.accessToken}}


# ─── Step 3: Tasks ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create a task
# @name createTask
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Set up CI/CD pipeline",
  "description": "Configure GitHub Actions for automated testing and deployment.",
  "priority": "High",
  "category": "DevOps",
  "dueDate": "2025-12-31T00:00:00Z"
}

###

@taskId = {{createTask.response.body.data.id}}

### Get all tasks (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?page=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=createdAt&sortDirection=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get all tasks — filter by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?status=InProgress&priority=High
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get all tasks — search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?search=pipeline
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get a single task
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update a task (partial — only send fields you want to change)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "InProgress",
  "title": "Set up CI/CD pipeline (updated)"
}

###

### AI summarize — generates summary, priority suggestion, and productivity tips
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/summarize
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Delete a task
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ─── Edge Cases ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Try to register with a duplicate email (expect 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "Secure@Pass1"
}

###

### Try to access tasks without a token (expect 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks

###

### Try to get a non-existent task (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
